      • transform

        protected abstract R transform(T t)
                        throws java.lang.Throwable
        Called to transform result of type T into the new result type (R). This method will be called at most once. After the first call, the result will be cached.
        パラメータ:
        t - original result
        戻り値:
        transformed result
        例外:
        java.lang.Throwable
